We have been in business since 2011 serving Peterborough and the Kawarthas. We are your full service HVAC Contractor and Duct Cleaning Specialists!

Whether you are looking to service or replace your existing equipment, we offer fast and reliable service.  Our knowledgable technicians are always available to provide you with the necessary information to help you chose the best equipment for your environment.

We carry the highest quality and most energy efficient systems on the market.

*****
